        "content": "<p>I was thinking about how it's rare to see anyone post in <a class=\"stream-topic\" data-stream-id=\"375707\" href=\"/#narrow/channel/375707-community/topic/hello.20I.27m.20new.20here/with/577335419\">#community &gt; hello I'm new here</a> <span aria-label=\"cry\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f622\" role=\"img\" title=\"cry\">:cry:</span> </p>\n<p>Should we set up a welcome message to encourage this? And say whatever else, of course.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/53090/WeEh0x-GfoF-fNV_KBHMlZ_A/Screenshot-2026-03-04-at-4.10.47PM.png\">Screenshot 2026-03-04 at 4.10.47 PM.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/53090/WeEh0x-GfoF-fNV_KBHMlZ_A/Screenshot-2026-03-04-at-4.10.47PM.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2026-03-04 at 4.10.47 PM.png\"><img data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"603x371\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/53090/WeEh0x-GfoF-fNV_KBHMlZ_A/Screenshot-2026-03-04-at-4.10.47PM.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div><p>Here are the docs: <a href=\"https://zulip.com/help/configure-a-custom-welcome-message\">https://zulip.com/help/configure-a-custom-welcome-message</a></p>",
